As a TFC affiliate, you will receive a personalized code which earns you income for recommending our tools to others

Your code will offer a discount to the people you give it to and will pay you a % of revenue

Final percentages are still to be determined but will be finalized by the time you make it to Basecamp

Initial affiliate products: Explorer memberships, SoleMates 



